def graph_pie(var):
    var = var.value_counts()
    var[7] = var[7:].values.sum()
    var.index[7]
    var.rename(index={var.index[7]:''}, inplace = True)
    var = var[:8]
    return var

def function_group_donation(x):
    if x > 0 and x <= 2:
        return '1-2 '
    elif x > 2 and x <= 10:
        return '3-10 '
    elif x > 10:
        return ' 10 '
